üì≤ Patient API Endpoints
1. üîê Login
POST /api/auth/login

Body:
{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

2. üìù Signup
POST /api/auth/signup

Body:
{
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "PATIENT"
}

3. Get Own Profile
GET /api/patient/profile

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

4.  Get Medications
GET /api/patient/medications

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

5. Mark Adherence
PATCH /api/patient/adherence

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

Body:
{
  "adherenceId": 123,
  "status": "complete"
}


6. Upload Adherence Proof
POST /api/patient/adherence/proof

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

FormData:
adherenceId: 123
status: complete
proof: (file upload)

7. Get Adherence Analytics
GET /api/patient/adherence/analytics

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

8. Assign Caretaker
PATCH /api/patient/select-caretaker

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

Body:
{
  "caretakerId": 1
}

üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è Caretaker API Endpoints
1. üîê Login
POST /api/auth/login

Body:
{
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

2. Signup
POST /api/auth/signup

Body:
{
  "name": "Bob",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "CARETAKER"
}

3. Get Own Profile
GET /api/caretaker/profile

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

4. Get All Caretakers (for Patient to choose)
GET /api/caretakers

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

5.  Get Assigned Patients
GET /api/caretaker/patients

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

6. Assign Medication to Patient
POST /api/caretaker/medications

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

Body:
{
  "patientId": 2,
  "name": "Paracetamol",
  "dosage": "500mg",
  "frequency": "Once daily",
  "durationDays": 7
}

7. Update Medication
PATCH /api/caretaker/medications/update

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

Body:
{
  "medicationId": 1,
  "name": "Updated Med",
  "dosage": "250mg",
  "frequency": "Twice daily",
  "durationDays": 10
}

8.  Delete Medication
DELETE /api/caretaker/medications/:medicationId

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

9. Get Adherence Analytics (for a patient)
GET /api/caretaker/adherence/analytics?patientId=2

Headers:
Authorization: Bearer <token>




